    Data from line transect survey of kangaroos

    nonstratified_farrar.Rd

    Traditional line transect distance sampling data set. Required fields are Transect, Length, Distance and group

    Usage

    data("nonstratified_farrar")

    Format

    A data frame with 373 observations on the following 6 variables.

    Stratum

    a factor with levels Farrar

    Area

    size of stratum

    Transect

    a factor with levels transect0 transect1 transect10 transect12 transect14 transect15 transect16 transect18 transect19 transect20 transect21 transect23 transect4 transect7 transect8

    Length

    transect length

    Distance

    perpendicular distance from transect

    group

    number of individuals in detected group
